title: Dubstep Jam
description:
Dubstep Jam is a real dubstep station for your improvisation. You can use it anywhere in the street jams or enjoying the headphones. Separately leased line drum, bass line, and of course fatty pads allow you to create the ambiance dubstep and Wobble bass turn it all into dubstep madness. Enjoy yourself, play with your friends in jams, dubstep sound is freedom. Excellence in the use of Dubstep Jam and you will always be dubstep rhythm master!

-= Features =-
- Multi Touch supported.
- Sound samples with professional equipment.
- Best dubstep station on your device.
- High quality sound samples.
- Enjoy the music .
- Use in street music jams.
- Maximum volume.
- Implemented a dynamic volume, now sound more lively.
- Added multisampling in Wobble mode.
